OL,8,GWhat happens when you don’t give up
OL,9,Gyour childhood dream of going to
OL,10,Gspace? As a teenager, I decided I
OL,11,Gwanted to be an astronaut. Since then,
OL,12,GI have tailored my career, my hobbies
OL,13,Gand my life experiences to achieving
OL,14,Gthat goal. Be that learning to fly,
OL,15,Gbecoming an analogue astronaut or
OL,16,Gworking as an engineer on some of the
OL,17,Gworld’s most complex engineering
OL,18,Gprojects. In this talk, I will
OL,19,Gdescribe my journey to becoming a
OL,20,Gspacecraft engineer and my life as an
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
